    "description": "Unified Agile ticket operations (EPIC, STORY, TASK) using a flat, single-field interface. Pass only top-level string arguments: action, item_id, item_type, field_name, field_value, parent_id, query. CREATE: action='create', item_type='EPIC|STORY|TASK', field_value=<short name/title>, parent_id=<epic or story UUID when creating a STORY or TASK>. READ: action='read', item_id=<UUID>. UPDATE: action='update', item_id=<UUID>, field_name=<exact DB field>, field_value=<new value>. SEARCH: action='search', item_type='EPIC|STORY|TASK', query=<search text>. COMMENT: action='comment', item_id=<UUID>, field_value=<comment text>. Always perform atomic, single-field updates by calling this tool once per field you wish to change. All actions return a structured JSON blob describing ok, action, item_type, item_id, data, and error.",
